# GhostAgent — Implementation Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A full-stack LinkedIn automation agent ("Digital Twin") with **25 files** across **6 phases**, built on top of the existing `computer-agent` codebase.

## Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    CLI[cli.py — Setup / Run / Review / Stats] --> Agent[agent.py — Orchestrator]
    Agent --> Schedule[scheduler.py — Sleep/Wake Cycle]
    Agent --> Guard[guardrails.py — Rate Limits SQLite]
    Agent --> Warmup[warmup.py — 48h Ghost Mode]
    
    Agent --> Nav[navigator.py — Non-Linear Navigation]
    Nav --> ACT[accessibility.py — ACT Extraction]
    Nav --> Human[human.py — Bézier / Jitter / Typo]
    Nav --> Browser[browser.py — Stealth Patchright]
    
    Agent --> Connect[connect.py — Connection Flow]
    Agent --> Interact[interact.py — Post Engagement]
    Agent --> Inbox[inbox.py — Smart Replies]
    
    Connect --> GW[ghostwriter.py — AI Messages]
    GW --> Vision[vision.py — Gemini + DeepSeek]
    GW --> Persona[persona.py — Style Clone]
    GW --> Diversity[diversity.py — Uniqueness]
    
    Agent --> Queue[approval_queue.py — Tinder Review]
```

