## Anti-Detection Features

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| **Bézier mouse paths** | Cubic curves with micro-jitters (2px tremor) |
| **Click pressure** | `mouseDown()` → 75-200ms delay → `mouseUp()` |
| **Overshoot** | 20% of clicks overshoot by 5-15px then correct |
| **Typing typos** | 3% chance of wrong key → backspace → correct |
| **Inertial scroll** | Fast start, gradual deceleration (trackpad physics) |
| **Content-aware dwell** | Reading speed = 180-280 WPM × word count |
| **Random detours** | 30% chance of "distraction" before target action |
| **Non-linear nav** | Never uses direct URLs — always search → click |
| **Session timing** | 15-45 min sessions, 2-5 min micro-breaks |
| **Sleep cycle** | 8am-11pm in user timezone, 8h offline |

## How to Run

```bash
cd /home/rishu/Documents/Codewave-Labs/computer-agent/ghost-agent
python -m venv venv && source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
patchright install chromium

# 1. First-time setup
python cli.py setup

# 2. Start warm-up (must run for 48h before outreach)
python cli.py warmup

# 3. Review AI-generated connection notes
python cli.py review

# 4. Start the agent
python cli.py run "John Doe" "Jane Smith"

# 5. Run continuously (sleep/wake cycle)
python cli.py run -c

# 6. Check stats
python cli.py stats
```
